product_name: Aqua Sphere Kayenne Smoke Lens Swim Goggles - Men's
long_description: The Aqua Sphere Kayenne Smoke Lens swim goggles use oversize lenses to enhance visibility. Scratch-resistant Plexisol(R) synthetic resin lenses help keep your vision clear with their antifog properties; plus, they offer 100% UVA and UVB protection. Smoke lenses offer high visibility outdoors or in bright light. Stabilizing nose bridge offers a comfortable and secure fit. Hypoallergenic silicone-gasket skirt creates a watertight seal and feels soft against skin. Aqua Sphere Kayenne Smoke Lens swim goggles secure the fit with a nonslip headstrap and easy-adjust, locking side buckles.
